教學方法 Teaching Strategies
      授課方式分為講義和研討兩部份，講義方面將探討英譯中翻譯相關理論，研討方面將進行實際例句或短文的演練與討論。
This course is designed with the two sections of lecture instruction and class discussion. The lecture instruction is focused on Chinese-English translation theory, and the class discussion is conducted on examples and exercises.        

		※請遵守智慧財產權觀念  不得不法影印
		 Please follow the Intellectual Property instruction and No illegal copy
	

課程教材 Course Material
	    1.本課程教學以講義為主，不採用單一教科書。
   Handouts, instead of a single textbook, will be used for this course.
2.本課程授課前一週利用Moodle教學平臺提供上課講義。
   Handouts will be available from Moodle one week ahead of each class.
3.請於每週上課前下載印出授課講義。
  It is recommended that weekly handouts be downloaded and printed-off before the start of each class.    

參考書目 References
	    孫述宇金聖華 英譯中 聯經出版社    

備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
■ 厚植人文素養及西洋文學、語言、文化及知識
 To cultivate their spirit of humanity and increase their knowledge of western literature, languages and cultures.
□ 培養獨立思考、團隊合作及思辨能力、發展關懷與服務精神
 To improve their capabilities for independent thinking, teamwork, and critical analysis and develop their civil concern and spirit of service
■ 擴展國際視野、接受多元文化及跨領域學習
 To broaden their global vision and accept diverse cultures and interdisciplinary 
learning.
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 具備人文素養及社會關懷與服務的能力
 Ability to provide social concern and service with a spirit of humanity.
□ 具備語言學、語言教學理論、知識與應用能力
 Ability to apply professionally the knowledge and theory of linguistics and language teaching.
■ 英外語溝通及應用能力
 Ability to demonstrate foreign language proficiency in various applications.
□ 多面向深入閱讀、賞析外國文學、語言、文化與藝術的能力
 Ability to appreciate and analyze foreign literatures, languages and cultures from multi-dimensional perspectives.
■ 適應多元文化與職場領域的知能
 Abiltiy to accomodate diverse cultures and professional fields.
□ 培養獨立及批判性思考、提問及解決問題的能力
 Ability to think independently and critically and to raise questions and solve problems.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       1.學生獲得翻譯理論的知識。
2.在課堂上學到翻譯技巧，具備翻譯能力應用在中英及英中翻譯上。
1.Students will know some translation theories.
2.Some tranlation skills will be acquired through lectures and practice.
3.Students are expected to be competent in rendering texts fron Chinese into English and vice versa .    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    本課程之建構旨在增進學生英翻中筆譯之知識與能力。授課內容介紹英中筆譯之基本觀念，技巧與原則，並教導學生如何運用中英文閱讀及寫作經驗，進行翻譯操作。本課程希望學生發展自我策略，分析解讀文本並處理常見之翻譯問題及相關因素，以期能夠完成滿意的翻譯作品。
This  course is designed for students to improve their knowledge and proficiency in English-Chinese translation. It introduces the basic concepts, skills and principles of English-Chinese translation and intstructs students to apply their reading and writing experiences to the practice of English-Chinese translation.  Students are encouraged to develop their own strategies to analyze texts and deal with general translation problems and relevant factors to work out satisfactory translations.    

